  {
    "url": "https://www.mallareddyuniversity.ac.in/about-iic/about-iic",
    "title": "Home | MR University",
    "headings": [
      "TM",
      "Why the IIC Model?",
      "Way Forward",
      "​(As per Telangana State Private Universities Act No.13 of 2020 and G.O.Ms.No.14,  Higher Education (UE) Department)",
      "360 DegreeVIRTUAL TOUR"
    ],
    "paragraphs": [
      "Malla Reddy University, HyderabadIn the year2018, theMinistry of Education (MoE),through itsInnovation Cell (MIC),launched theInstitution’s Innovation Council (IIC)program in collaboration withAICTE. This initiative is designed forHigher Educational Institutions (HEIs)tosystematically foster a culture of innovation and a start-up ecosystemacross educational institutions in India.",
      "Objective of IICThe primary objective of IICs is to engage a large number of faculty, students, and staff invarious innovation and entrepreneurship-related activities, including:",
      "Project handling and management at pre-incubation/incubation stages",
      "This engagement aims to establish and stabilize a strong innovation andentrepreneurship ecosystem within HEIs.",
      "The IIC framework was developed toaddress key challengesobserved in HEIs:",
      "Lack of coordination in mobilizing and utilizing resources",
      "Underutilization of the creative and entrepreneurial potential of yout",
      "Fully integrateddigital platformfor coordination and reporting",
      "Over the past few years, the IIC initiative has proven to be sustainable and scalable, making a tangible impact on India's innovation ecosystem. Notably, India’s improved rank to48th position in the Global Innovation Index (GII)reflects these collective efforts.",
      "TheInstitution’s Innovation Council (IIC)was officially established atMalla Reddy University, Hyderabadduring a meeting held onAugust 6, 2022,in theVice Chancellor’s Conference Room.",
      "The following updated members were nominated asoffice bearersfor organizing andexecuting IIC activities at the university:",
      "Conduct structured I&E activities throughout the academic year",
      "Foster a spirit of innovation among students and faculty",
      "Support student-led start-ups and mentor entrepreneurial ventures",
      "Strengthen collaboration with industries and innovation hubs",
      "Together, we envision Malla Reddy University as a center of excellence in innovation,incubation, and entrepreneurship.",
      "Maisammaguda, Dulapally,Hyderabad, Telangana 500100Phone: 94971-94971, 91778-78365",
