    "paragraphs": [
      "B.Sc. - Emergency Medicine & Critical Care Technology",
      "B.Sc. - Bio-Technology, Bio-Chemistry, Microbiology",
      "B.Sc. - Clinical Nutrition, Dietetics & Food Science",
      "Malla Reddy University (MRU), the first Private University sanctioned by Telangana State Government (GO MS No: 1, Dated 20.5.2020/TS Act No. 13 of 2020), under the aegis of Malla Reddy Group of Institutions, Hyderabadbeing the pioneers in running educational institutions for the last two decades announces admissions to full-time courses in Under-graduate (UG), Post-graduate (PG), Ph.D programmes offered for the academic year 2022-2023, to create a fulfilling environment for imparting education to the students, integrating the intellectual, technical, human and artistic-cultural skills thus enabling their development and full potential as an industry ready intellectual.",
      "All eligible Candidates are informed that, the admission process of all the programmes through Joint Entrance Examination JEE (Mains)/State Common Entrance Examinations/ Malla Reddy University Common Entrance Test (MRUCET) Conducted by the University/ Qualifying Exam on merit for all categories.",
