  {
    "url": "https://www.mallareddyuniversity.ac.in/placements",
    "title": "Placements | MR University",
    "headings": [
      "TM",
      "PLACEMENTS",
      "Training, Certifications & Placements",
      "​(As per Telangana State Private Universities Act No.13 of 2020 and G.O.Ms.No.14,  Higher Education (UE) Department)",
      "360 DegreeVIRTUAL TOUR"
    ],
    "paragraphs": [
      "Malla Reddy University has a well laid-out systematic process of meeting student’s career aspirations and the corporate expectations. The Placement department functions as a bridge builder between the University’s Schools, Industries and Students. The process is transparent and commences with the uploading students profiles on placement portal. Each student, faculty coordinator and Training and Placement official has access to the portal.",
      "A result oriented approach is DNA of our placement cell. We have ensured that every stream of engineering and other disciplines of our University is aptly represented in their core domains. All the senior members of our placement cell have more than a decade of industrial and academic exposure, which enables our students to get placed in top-notch companies of national and international arena.​",
      "The experienced members know the exact requirements of a particular sector and the job. Working in close association with the training cell, the grooming of our students happens with an objective of a sure placement.",
      "We regularly observe the on-going market trends in order to make the students familiar with the latest happenings in the Industry.",
      "We organize and participate in business events with an aim to stay connected with the coveted companies.",
      "We regularly invite the Industrial stalwarts from different industries as guest lecturers. This helps our students to gain first-hand knowledge about the industry practices, etc. We also receive inputs from these industry leaders that help us to bring in timely changes to our course material and practical training.",
      "Few of the companies where our students are going to be associated with: Tata, Wipro, Cognizant, Infosys, IBM, Tech Mahindra, Capgemini, Polaris, Amazon, Mindtree, Hyundai, NTT Data, Sutherland, Value Labs, Excers, Cyient, Gspann, ZenQ, etc.",
      "To know more about our training and placement cell, you may send us an email onplacements@mallareddyuniversity.ac.in.",
      "CodeTantra is a tech-startup company which has developed a Cloud Based Automated Programming Tutor that builds coding abilities through an interactive, learn by doing methodology. With a pursuit to revolutionize the way technology is taught in classrooms, the company offers automated online training of programs for programming languages like Java, Selenium 2.0, Big data + Hadoop, C ,HTML & CSS.",
      "We the malla Reddy University associated with Codetantra in the process of adopting self ;learning coding courses through E-Learning. As a Part of this association we hosted an awareness program about codetantra and how it is beneficial for the student community in the process of E-Learning.",
      "Malla Reddy University has taken initiative to enhance the employability skills of students through organizing Group Discussion, Personal & Technical Interviews and Soft Skills to suit the requirements of Multi-national organizations.",
      "Certification Courses Offered atMalla Reddy University:",
      "Microsoft Innovation Center for Technology Training (MIC) and Certification.",
      "Business English Certification(BEC), University of Cambridge, UK",
      "Oxford Achiever’s Certification, Oxford University Press, for communication skills.",
      "Big Data Analytics and R-Programming Certification Course",
      "Organizing Certification courses such as CISCO, .Net, JAVA, CATIA, Pro-E, MATLAB etc.",
      "Career guidance and counseling for higher education",
      "WHY MALLA REDDY UNIVERSITY SHOULD BE YOUR FIRST CHOICE ?",
      "We enhance employability of students by equipping them with an array of skills like Group Discussions, Personal and Technical interviews and soft skills to meet the requirements of multinational companies and to make them technologically and professionally competent engineers.",
      "We expose the students to the corporate work culture by organizing Workshops, Professional Seminars, Guest Lectures and Industrial Training by experienced professionals.",
      "Research and Development is an integral part of the academic activities of Malla Reddy University. MALLA REDDY UNIVERSITY R&D cell is one of the wings of the Institute which facilitates, channelizes, records, and regulates all the academic, sponsored, collaborative research projects and consultancy works in the Institute. In a world increasingly propelled by technology, academic research forms the mainspring of a nation’s economic growth. MALLA REDDY UNIVERSITY R&D cell aspires to transform the lives of young budding engineers, research scholars and faculty through their innovative ideas to contribute for research at academic level. MALLA REDDY UNIVERSITY R&D cell is closely working with core industries to train the students in this direction. This objective will be very close to the heart of the industry in the direction of producing ready to be employed engineers. The key goal of the Institute is to provide a creative atmosphere in which higher studies and research thrive amongst the faculty and students. It also promotes and manages Institute-Industry interaction.",
      "Maisammaguda, Dulapally,Hyderabad, Telangana 500100Phone: 94971-94971, 91778-78365",
      "info@mallareddyuniversity.ac.inadmissions@mallareddyuniversity.ac.in",
